{"tid":658219,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以出港譯說 唔要用普通話譯","createTime":"2018-05-08T19:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T07:00:29.000Z","uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"360fec61c1fa9a4f0487de61eb7c755875d84823","tid":658219,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:11:35.000Z","msg":"只有長遠一路出書，先可以有效記錄低我地既文字"},{"pid":"7882e96c4e4512bde9cf3b3389991b4a3984f89f","tid":658219,"uid":18605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T20:46:40.000Z","msg":"係咪打漏左個小字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔太明你個港譯係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怕get錯就將我諗嘅都講哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你所謂嘅普通話譯係我地都用左咁多年嘅書面語的話我覺得冇乜必要<br />\n因為書面語=/=普通話<br />\n普通話其實都有口語存在 同書面語唔同<br />\n<br />\n舉個例<br />\n<br />\n粵：你唔好喺度鳩噏啦<br />\n普：你別在這兒瞎逼逼了<br />\n書：你別要在這裡胡說了<br />\n<br />\n定還是你想講嘅港譯係指一啲名稱嘅翻譯？<br />\n例如我地香港譯 碧咸<br />\n普通話就叫 貝克漢姆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果樓主講呢方面的話我絕對贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時睇書突然間睇到個唔知乜嘅字 查下先知原來係因為跟咗普通話譯法所以認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然有多啲港譯出書對廣東話傳承都係好事來嘅 無論邊方面都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700d7eed718bf64cd0d9c443cedb69ad920dbc21","tid":658219,"uid":45657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7882e96c4e4512bde9cf3b3389991b4a3984f89f","tid":658219,"uid":18605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"